    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/e399ec80933eb1fda25aa63c97dd08c9.webp?t=1767227138\" width=576 height=41 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/a82498af28b90c65ca77fa29d8ff3645.poster.avif?t=1767227138\" width=480 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/a82498af28b90c65ca77fa29d8ff3645.webm?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/a82498af28b90c65ca77fa29d8ff3645.mp4?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Treasure 'n Trio</strong> 是一款基于著名解谜游戏“推箱子”的单人解谜游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家以格子单位移动，推动各种物体，并与各种解谜装置互动，以推进游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/34a11b828706417d4ade7544fc0d56e4.webp?t=1767227138\" width=576 height=41 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/955801e978dc703f7abca6264311542c.poster.avif?t=1767227138\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/955801e978dc703f7abca6264311542c.webm?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/955801e978dc703f7abca6264311542c.mp4?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以操控三个角色。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以力量解决一切的战士</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无视危险因素的盗贼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有瞬间移动魔法但胆小的魔法师</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅靠单一角色无法解决谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请灵活运用三个角色，合理分配他们的能力，来解决所遇到的难题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/d92f38a43bf7f7243d1470533363e5c2.webp?t=1767227138\" width=576 height=41 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/4b22a50ee52a40dcb03de2ad8536a316.poster.avif?t=1767227138\" width=480 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/4b22a50ee52a40dcb03de2ad8536a316.webm?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/4b22a50ee52a40dcb03de2ad8536a316.mp4?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从宁静的森林到熔岩翻滚的危险区域，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有多种主题的世界不断带来新的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个世界中，体验独特的怪物与解谜装置吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/2d9213120ed2272ecfc781cadbb9d26f.webp?t=1767227138\" width=576 height=41 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/84632988d4028a88e1fced787da6e80e.poster.avif?t=1767227138\" width=480 height=454 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/84632988d4028a88e1fced787da6e80e.webm?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/84632988d4028a88e1fced787da6e80e.mp4?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅途的终点，往往藏有宝物的踪影。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都有不同的、有些搞怪的宝物等你来收集。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能收集齐所有宝物吗？试试看吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/8ae62f05d4382f0bb7826ba7f6359b84.webp?t=1767227138\" width=576 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/b2ed8d28a2ac9f27f41f6ef67d67a5b4.poster.avif?t=1767227138\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/b2ed8d28a2ac9f27f41f6ef67d67a5b4.webm?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214530/extras/b2ed8d28a2ac9f27f41f6ef67d67a5b4.mp4?t=1767227138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了追求更高难度的挑战，特别准备了支线任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在特定条件下攻略相同的关卡，这是一种高难度模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请勇敢挑战支线任务吧！</p>",
